        }
    }
}
```

**Step-by-Step Nested Trace:**

$$
\begin{aligned}
\text{Step 1:} \quad & \text{Enter OUTER try → Print "Outer try start"} \\
\text{Step 2:} \quad & \text{Enter INNER try → Integer.parseInt("abc") throws NumberFormatException} \\
\text{Step 3:} \quad & \text{INNER catch executes → "Inner catch: For input string: \"abc\""} \\
\text{Step 4:} \quad & \text{INNER finally executes → "Inner finally"} \\
\text{Step 5:} \quad & \text{Continue in OUTER try → Evaluate 10/0 → ArithmeticException} \\
\text{Step 6:} \quad & \text{OUTER catch executes → "Outer catch: / by zero"} \\
\text{Step 7:} \quad & \text{OUTER finally executes → "Outer finally"} \\
